title: Chris Kwiecinski - 5 / 25 / 23
body_text:
Have Mizzou men’s and women’s hoops gotten enough from the transfer portal this offseason?
Chris Kwiecinski of the Columbia Daily Tribune joined the Big Show on Thursday to talk about the gains and losses this offseason for both squads. Plus, we discuss the football home opener getting moved to Thursday again, and the end of the Mizzou spring sports season.
